      "content": "thanks but friends and family... they all just look at me with that pitying face. it's exhausting. every time they say \"it gets better\" i just want to scream because it doesn't feel like it ever will. it's like the color has been drained out of everything. i'm just so tired of the noise of being alive when he's gone.",
